x=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 15, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wla1665702773104.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wla1665702773104.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wla1665702773104.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wla1665702773104\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Split Views in the\n      Script Editor</h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wla1665702773104__split_views_in_the_script_editor_17735\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Write Script worksheet allows you to open two views of the Script Editor, each\n      with its own Structure pane and Code Editor.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"wla1665702773104__topic_d4256e1_d4257e1_d4258e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wla1665702773104__p_d4259e1_d4260e1_d4261e1\">This can be useful when you want to view and edit the code in two places or two objects at the same time. For example, you may want to copy and paste some code from one place to another, or edit both a call to a script module and the called script module at the same time.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"wla1665702773104__section_w663ab1b5b5_w664ab1b5_w665ab1\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wla1665702773104__li_d1709e1_d1710e1_d1711e1\">To open a secondary Script Editor, click the Split\n               View icon. <figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"wla1665702773104__fig_nr5_v5m_lzb\">\n<img alt=\"Multiple ScriptEditor icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"wla1665702773104__image_or5_v5m_lzb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/multiplescriptviewbtns.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wla1665702773104__li_d1715e1_d1716e1_d1717e1\">You can then have each view show a different section\n               of code. <figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"wla1665702773104__fig_ykb_y5m_lzb\">\n<img alt=\"Multiple Script Editors in the Write Script worksheet\" class=\"image\" id=\"wla1665702773104__image_zkb_y5m_lzb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/multiscripteditor.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"wla1665702773104__li_d1718e1_d1719e1_d1720e1\">Use the 1 and 2 buttons to expand the view and\n               switch between the views.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533396\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533396\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Split Views in the Script Editor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 15, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Split Views in the Script Editor The Write Script worksheet allows you to open two views of the Script Editor, each with its own Structure pane and Code Editor. This can be useful when you want to view and edit the code in two places or two objects at the same time. For example, you may want to copy and paste some code from one place to another, or edit both a call to a script module and the called script module at the same time. To open a secondary Script Editor, click the Split View icon. You can then have each view show a different section of code. Use the 1 and 2 buttons to expand the view and switch between the views. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}